// ─────────── Fixed Assets register + periodic audit ───────────
// Captures non-purchasable items (tables, chairs, sofas, fans, fridges …) the
// outlet owns. These don't flow through Purchase Orders — the owner just logs
// what's there and then audits periodically. Variance between expected and
